Introduction

Thank you everyone for joining us in our 1st edition of Gurans Cup. Congratulations to Texas FC Blue in regular and Nepal Seattle FC in 35+ category for winning the tournament. Looking forward to seeing you all next year.

Regular Category:

  • Winner: Texas FC Blue
  • Runner Up: Dallas Gurkhas Red
  • MVP: Monoj Chuwan (Texas FC Blue)
  • Best GoalKeeper: Parth Jung Thapa (Dallas Gurkhas Red)

35+ Category:

  • Winner: Nepal Seattle FC
  • Runner Up: DFW Himalayas FC
  • MVP: Umesh Pandey (Nepal Seattle FC)
  • Best GoalKeeper:Sajal Nepal (Nepal Seattle FC)
